# Assignment:2

Monica's Situation:
Monica Moore is applying for a new accounting job in ABC, Inc. She wants to write a professional email to the job recruiter at the company,
but doesn't know their name. She wants to give a good first impression as well as sound professional.

# Sample letter for Job Application.

Subject: Job Application : Monica Moore

Dear Hiring Manager,

My name is Monica Moore. I am writing to express my interest in seeking the accounting job at your profound company.I will be great fit for 
this position beacuse I am skilled in various word-processing and accounting software. I also have great communication skills. My resume 
includes more details of my skills and education.

I look forward to the opportunity to speak with you further. Thank you for your time and consideration.

Regards,

Monica Moore

Tel:+1-123-7890

